{"type":"message","id":"c3554218","parentId":"36ca4840","timestamp":"2026-03-24T03:30:01.393Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:20ad25e9-a93b-4554-9c04-ac4c8f1f3016 飞书备份方案持续研究] 请研究飞书多维表格（Bitable）备份方案的可行性：\n\n## 研究任务\n\n1. **分析失败原因**\n   - 检查 feishu_bitable_create_app API 调用参数\n   - 尝试不同的参数组合（folder_token、name 等）\n   - 记录具体错误信息\n\n2. **替代方案探索**\n   - 方案 A：云文档 + 表格块（用 feishu_doc create_table）\n   - 方案 B：使用现有 Bitable（如果用户已有）\n   - 方案 C：云盘文件备份（JSON 原始数据）\n\n3. **实践测试**\n   - 尝试用 feishu_doc 在文档中创建表格\n   - 测试表格内容写入\n   - 验证是否可实现类似 Bitable 的结构化存储\n\n4. **输出报告**\n   - 哪种方案最可行？\n   - 需要什么额外权限？\n   - 推荐什么备份策略？\n\n## 记录要求\n\n写入文件：`memory/飞书备份研究日志.md`\n- 研究时间\n- 尝试的方法\n- 成功/失败\n- 下一步计划\n\n记住：目标是找到可靠的飞书备份方案，不一定要用 Bitable！\nCurrent time: Tuesday, March 24th, 2026 — 11:30 (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-03-24 03:30 UTC\n\nReturn your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself."}],"timestamp":1774323001392}}
{"type":"message","id":"37b4ac45","parentId":"c3554218","timestamp":"2026-03-24T03:30:11.966Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"这是一个关于飞书备份方案研究的任务。我需要：\n\n1. 首先检查之前的失败记录，了解 feishu_bitable_create_app API 调用为什么失败\n2. 尝试不同的 API 调用方式\n3. 探索替代方案（云文档表格、现有 Bitable、云盘文件备份）\n4. 实践测试各种方案\n5. 输出研究报告到 memory/飞书备份研究日志.md\n\n让我先搜索一下之前的相关记录和错误信息。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_06a9550e415d4e5091802ea0","name":"memory_search","arguments":{"query":"飞书备份 Bitable feishu_bitable_create_app 失败 错误","maxResults":10}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774323001392}}
